flowchart LR
  service[Server-only planning service] --> adapter[Gemini adapter]
  adapter --> request[Prompt + ComponentContract + happy-path props]
  request --> gemini[gemini-2.5-flash-lite]
  gemini --> structured[Structured JSON response]
  structured --> zod[AiPlanningProposalSchema]
  zod --> trusted[Trusted StateStorm materializers]
  missing[Missing key, quota, timeout, refusal, invalid output, provider error] --> fallback[Deterministic fallback]
  trusted --> plan[Validated RunPlan v1]
  fallback --> plan
